      <title>百事公司将再投资 4 亿美元在越南建设两家新工厂</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/pepsico-invest-400-mln-more-two-new-plants-vietnam-2024-03-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南政府周五表示，美国食品和饮料制造商百事可乐公司已承诺在越南追加投资 4 亿美元，在该国建设两座由可再生能源驱动的新工厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/pepsico-invest-400-mln-more-two-new-plants-vietnam-2024-03-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 04:42:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>地球物理机构称印度尼西亚爪哇岛发生里氏6.1级地震</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/magnitude-61-quake-strikes-off-indonesias-java-island-geophysics-agency-says-2024-03-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚地球物理机构 (BKMG) 表示，印度尼西亚爪哇岛沿岸周五发生了 6.1 级地震，震源深度为 10 公里（6.21 英里）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/magnitude-61-quake-strikes-off-indonesias-java-island-geophysics-agency-says-2024-03-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 04:39:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>独家：消息人士称，英国法律总局搁置中国营业执照计划并裁员</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/uks-legal-general-shelves-china-business-license-plan-cuts-headcount-sources-say-2024-03-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国保险公司和资产管理公司 Legal &amp;两名消息人士称，通用汽车已搁置了获得中国营业执照的计划，并将在岸员工人数减少了一半以上，加入了在不确定的市场中缩减规模的全球金融公司行列。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/uks-legal-general-shelves-china-business-license-plan-cuts-headcount-sources-say-2024-03-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 04:32:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国的悲观情绪让亚洲降息的欢呼失去了活力</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，中国股市一片红海，人民币大幅下跌，拖累了亚洲整体情绪，并削弱了瑞士央行出人意料的降息举措，令投资者押注谁可能是下一个降息者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 02:25:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者寻求“套利”，美元坚挺</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steadfast-investors-seek-carry-2024-03-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美元周五将连续第二周大幅上涨，即使日本加息也无法撼动美元的走势，因为投资者认为美国利率处于高位且尚未下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steadfast-investors-seek-carry-2024-03-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 01:20:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国科学家在实验室培育珊瑚以恢复退化的珊瑚礁</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/thai-scientists-breed-coral-labs-restore-degraded-reefs-2024-03-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一个繁星点点的夜晚，四名泰国海洋生物学家潜水穿过该国南部一座岛屿附近的浅水区，数十亿粉红色斑点从海底漂浮起来，这是一年仅发生一次的奇观。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/thai-scientists-breed-coral-labs-restore-degraded-reefs-2024-03-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 01:17:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝中社称，朝鲜派遣代表团访问中国、越南、老挝</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-sends-delegation-china-vietnam-laos-kcna-says-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[官方媒体朝中社周五表示，朝鲜已向中国、越南和老挝派遣了一个代表团，这个孤立的国家在 COVID-19 封锁后扩大了外交接触。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-sends-delegation-china-vietnam-laos-kcna-says-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 23:11:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>长江集团李嘉诚表示香港需要维护金融中心地位</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/ck-groups-li-says-hong-kong-needs-safeguard-financial-hub-status-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[长江集团董事长李泽钜周四表示，经过多年的动荡，香港政府需要保护香港的国际金融中心地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/ck-groups-li-says-hong-kong-needs-safeguard-financial-hub-status-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 12:35:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BAE 赢得 AUKUS 潜艇项目，澳大利亚拨款数十亿美元用于海军基础设施</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/australia-earmarks-billions-naval-infrastructure-bae-wins-aukus-submarine-work-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚周四表示，根据 AUKUS 安全协议，将斥资数十亿美元在国内和英国建造核动力潜艇的码头、造船厂和工厂，并指定英国 BAE Systems 帮助建造这些潜艇。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/australia-earmarks-billions-naval-infrastructure-bae-wins-aukus-submarine-work-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 11:33:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国称，悬挂韩国国旗的船只在日本倾覆，造成九人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/nine-dead-after-south-korean-flagged-vessel-capsized-off-japan-skorea-says-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国外交部周四表示，一艘悬挂韩国国旗的船只在日本附近倾覆，造成至少九人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/nine-dead-after-south-korean-flagged-vessel-capsized-off-japan-skorea-says-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 10:39:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
